About Wellness Whisper : Wellness Whisper is a specialized mental health consulting firm that focuses on the overall mental wellness. One of the core objectives of our work is to ensure that people feel safe and comfortable while speaking about their mental health issues. We provide individual consultations regarding a number of topics concerning mental health while developing and publishing unique articles and blogs to the needs of our clients.

